author: Mícheál Lehane
title: Seanad count should be in private, says Cathaoirleach
description: The Cathaoirleach of the Seanad has made an impassioned plea to candidates not to attend the Upper House election count which begins on Monday.
content:
The Cathaoirleach of the Seanad has made an impassioned plea to candidates not to attend the Upper House election count which begins on Monday.
Denis O'Donovan has spent the weekend contacting candidates to urge them and their agents not to attend the count … [+1954 chars]
